---
<section class="px-container-padding mb-section-gap">
  <div class="relative w-full h-[75vh] clip-angular clip-angular-border p-[1px]">
    <div class="absolute inset-[1px] overflow-hidden bg-[#0d0d0d] clip-inner">
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center"
        style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDiOOkOD-wGFrmjt4IobyihVsKmSxpoATsWP8FFHqfUjPriEe6ZLr-711aX4qcmMVsDRuU3PTc_qw1Mm8EtGkPMiMJhBZUPJ8KoB04TK9ujgz4V32wcckHQJdleg8pINGrEKJCX64EwETi7r_hjxjLpdbH6JO2QObHlW-A2Cr0fB92dhV_Qeoj9b6fy4vO-uBtu-i1pJtdx9xKEYOHGoYkb4ov8eGGKaWZbupnkUIGzPYoiI0pxrE-BEMQ7mCemajS4q9GDWxBUNUMj9Q')"
      ></div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-l from-[#0d0d0d]/95 via-[#0d0d0d]/60 to-[#0d0d0d]/30"></div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 p-16 flex flex-col justify-center max-w-4xl items-end text-right ml-auto">
        <h1 class="font-display-lg text-display-lg text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          Eficiencia / <br />
          <span class="font-headline-italic text-headline-italic text-orange italic">Energética Industrial</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-10 max-w-xl">
          Diseñamos, proyectamos e instalamos sistemas fotovoltaicos a gran escala y soluciones de almacenamiento inteligente para plantas de manufactura y centros logísticos.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-end">
          <button class="rounded-none border border-primary px-6 py-3 text-primary hover:bg-primary hover:text-black transition-colors uppercase font-label-mono text-sm">Solicitar Auditoría Técnica</button>
          <button class="rounded-none border border-white/20 px-6 py-3 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors uppercase font-label-mono text-sm">Descargar Dossier Corporativo</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 flex w-full md:w-auto md:min-w-[700px] bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-xl border-t border-l border-white/10">
        <span class="flex-1 text-center py-6 border-r border-white/10 font-label-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white">Fotovoltaicos</span>
        <span class="flex-1 text-center py-6 border-r border-white/10 font-label-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white">BESS</span>
        <span class="flex-1 text-center py-6 font-label-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white">Eficiencia Energética</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
